{"tid":1245751,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[BE WATER]添馬政府總部明日暫停開放","createTime":"2019-06-20T12:29:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-20T13:47:12.000Z","uid":41389,"like":223,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"10aafe1955c6bb0af0e64bb1f16147828a5ba2a5","tid":1245751,"uid":41389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T12:29:30.000Z","msg":"添馬政府總部明日暫停開放<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n基於保安考慮，明日（六月二十一日）添馬政府總部暫停開放。 <br />\n<br />\n同事無需返回政府總部工作，並應按照所屬決策局或部門的應變計劃工作。所有訪客活動亦會延期或取消。 <br />\n<br />\n完<br />\n2019年6月20日（星期四）<br />\n香港時間20時18分"},{"pid":"876d797ed2981960d48cd8d99add7680cbdc3f9f","tid":1245751,"uid":41389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T12:30:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b36455285b53642858c534bd2429b47a618fdf2","tid":1245751,"uid":41389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T12:30:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3139ec3a40e747f0c271f59e806794aa7d2469d5","tid":1245751,"uid":65888,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T12:31:06.000Z","msg":"Source?"},{"pid":"33f78eac753f70c4f1f903a1fdf90daea4dcd017","tid":1245751,"uid":251925,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T12:31:41.000Z","msg":"渣ga"},{"pid":"566dbfe81dd18ed378858301a635fefed152abab","tid":1245751,"uid":54593,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T12:31:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201906/20/P2019062000689.htm\"